name: Vintage Elegant Feather Headband
description:
Beautifully hand-crafted hair accessory, features bright orange and brown Goose feathers adorned on top of a golden/bronze padded headband. I have included a vintage brooch to add charm to this lovely piece, which makes this one-of-a-kind.

The headband is extremely comfortable and the color of these feathers are quite unique. Creates a flapper-esque vibe.

Perfect for any vintage kitten!

name: Art Nouveau Coral Floral Charm Necklace- Jolie Fleur
description:
Title: Jolie Fleur Necklace

Hand-crafted Antique Bronze Cross Chain necklace. Featuring a beautiful light coral pink rose cabochon placed on an antiqued brass filigree flower stamping. White and Pink floral cameo placed on an antique gold filigree stamping. Features 6 simulate ivory colored pearls attached by using Antiqued Pure Brass Wire.

Lovely and dainty!

name: Art Nouveau Purple Charleston Lady Vintage Necklace
description:
Title: Charleston Lady

This is an Art Nouveau inspired necklace that I have hand-crafted.

This Antique Bronze Cross Chain necklace is adorned with a Brass Victorian Pendant with Purple Amethyst Glass Jewel Cabochon attached to a 16mm Antique Copper Square Filigree Stamping Connector by using Antiqued Pure Brass Wire. 12 beautiful simulate pearls at center of necklace. 2 Golden Bronze Lucite & 2 Clear Lucite beads and floral antique gold spacers. Lovely and one-of-a-kind beauty.

This necklace length is approx 16.5" and is closed by Antique Bronze Lobster Clasps.
